    FROST_MAGE
    BREWMASTER
    WINDWALKER
    MISTWEAVER
    HOLY_PRIEST
    DISCIPLINE
    SHADOW
    ASSASSINATION
    OUTLAW
    SUBTLETY
    ELEMENTAL
    ENHANCEMENT
    RESTORATION_SHAMAN
    AFFLICTION
    DEMONOLOGY
    DESTRUCTION
    ARMS
    FURY
    PROTECTION_WARRIOR
